name: title
Kononenko 12mm beam JTBEQ 12 wks: Kinematic of 12-week-old JTBEQ mice walking on a 12 mm wide beam

name: description
Kononenko 12mm beam JTBEQ 12 wks: Original SIMI videos, DeepLabCut-tracked videos and csv files of body kinematics of 12-week-old VGAT-Cre;Atg5flox/flox mice walking on a wide 12 mm beam. Mixed group of control and mutant mice. Individual trials for each mouse are recorded from 8 cameras and metadata for synchronization is stored as *.smp files.
